cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with a wireless IoT network with UAVs and applies reinforcement learning to optimize the network's energy sustainability and capacity. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also proposes a Constrained Deep Reinforcement Learning algorithm, which suggests the paper may belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with control and optimization, which may place it in cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
